<h3>Midterm Assessment</h3>
<p>The project for the midterm assessment was to write a Chinese Zodiac trivia quiz. Basic project requirements included: a combination of text and multiple choice input options, fields for the taker's name and email address, data validation for all form fields, the quiz be self correcting, and the quiz had to tell the user how he did when he took it. Additionally, by adding more backend features, the score achieved on the assessment could be increased.</p>
